  &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Source: Official Letter No. &lt;a href="https://binhphu.vinhlong.gov.vn/Portals/1257/722.pdf"&gt;722.25/JICA-GI&lt;/a&gt; dated September 3, 2025 of the Japan International Cooperation Agency (JICA) Office in Vietnam&lt;/p&gt;

