  &lt;h2&gt;1. Introduction to the JICA ‚ÄúSDGs Global Leader‚Äù Scholarship&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;The ‚ÄúSDGs Global Leader‚Äù program is part of the JICA Knowledge Co-Creation Program under the Official Development Assistance (ODA) framework of the Government of Japan. The program aims to develop high-quality human resources capable of contributing to the formulation and implementation of sustainable development policies. Study duration: 2 years (Master's) or 3 years (Doctoral).&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Policy capacity development:&lt;/strong&gt; Learn from Japan's unique development experience.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expand international network:&lt;/strong&gt; Connect with future leaders from 111 countries.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full scholarship:&lt;/strong&gt; Covers tuition, living expenses, airfare, and insurance.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Special JICA-DSP program:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate in activities, internships at Japanese public/private organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h2&gt;2. Who can apply for the JICA Scholarship?&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;The scholarship is for young/mid-career government officials, lecturers, or researchers who can contribute to policy and social development in Vietnam.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;h3&gt;‚úÖ Eligibility requirements:&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Vietnamese citizen eligible for Japanese ODA.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Currently working in a government agency, research institute, or university.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Age: ‚â§35 (Master's), ‚â§40 (Doctoral) as of April 1, 2026.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Degree: Bachelor's (for Master's) or Master's (for Doctoral).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;English: TOEFL iBT ‚â•80 or IELTS ‚â•6.5.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Must be physically present in Japan throughout the course.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h3&gt;‚ùå Not eligible if:&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
