      &lt;li&gt;Currently receiving or will receive another scholarship.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Belong to the military or related organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Cannot be physically present in Japan.&lt;/li&gt;
