  &lt;h2&gt;4. JICA Application Guide&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Applicants must be nominated by their home institution and approved by the Government of Vietnam. Applications must be submitted through the Ministry of Finance of Vietnam no later than October 22, 2025.&lt;/p&gt;

