    DIGITISING MEDICAL RESEARCH: INTEGRATING ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE AND BIOBANKING FOR ACCELERATED DISCOVERY
  &lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://cbiit.webex.com/webappng/sites/cbiit/meeting/register/e9797166f4df411485ea03bc6050a985?ticket=4832534b00000007410103467bbb9fe6eae9bf4d27789b6ec7cc5fd886660b279888ccd469760374&timestamp=1759833481004&RGID=r9eca86620bdd4e16c1f14910c757478f&isAutoPopRegisterForm=false" class="btn-register" target="_blank"&gt;
    Register Now
