    &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
      &lt;span class="timeline-date"&gt;Jun 2026&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Official results&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
      &lt;span class="timeline-date"&gt;07/09/2026&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Offer of admission deadline&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
      &lt;span class="timeline-date"&gt;Sep‚ÄìOct 2026&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Departure for studies&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h2&gt;9. Why choose Chevening?&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Full scholarship covering all expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Study at the world's most prestigious universities.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Network of over 50,000 alumni worldwide.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Become a cultural bridge between Vietnam and the UK.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="final-note"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start preparing today!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
    Chevening is not just a scholarship ‚Äì it's a gateway to becoming a global leader.&lt;br&gt;
    If you have ambition, vision, and a commitment to contributing to your homeland, don't hesitate to apply for Chevening 2025/2026!&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

