  &lt;h2&gt;6. Erasmus Mundus Scholarship value&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Living allowance: ‚Ç¨1,400/month (24 months = ‚Ç¨33,600)&lt;/li&gt;
