      &lt;li&gt;Total value: approximately ‚Ç¨50,000‚Äì55,000/2 years&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h2&gt;7. Application guide&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ol&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Create an account at &lt;a href="https://emundus.izp.cm-uj.krakow.pl" target="_blank"&gt;emundus.izp.cm-uj.krakow.pl&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
