  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h2&gt;8. Selection criteria&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Motivation and career goals ‚Äì 30%&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Academic achievement ‚Äì 25%&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Professional/volunteer experience ‚Äì 20%&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;International experience ‚Äì 15%&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Communication skills ‚Äì 10%&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;h2&gt;9. Reasons to choose Europubhealth+&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;div class="highlight-box"&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Study at 8 leading EU universities ‚Äì recognized as a "Master of Excellence".&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;International dual degree, study in 2‚Äì3 countries.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Integrates biostatistics, epidemiology, data science.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Global alumni network, internships at WHO, NGOs, research institutes.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Strong financial support and wide career opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="final-note"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start preparing today!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
    Europubhealth+ is not just a master's program ‚Äì it's a journey to becoming a global public health leader.&lt;br&gt;
    Whether you come from Medicine, Pharmacy, Biology, or Economics, Law, Sociology ‚Äì the program welcomes everyone.&lt;br&gt;
    Erasmus Mundus Scholarship application deadline: &lt;strong&gt;01/08/2026&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì Don't miss out!&lt;/p&gt;
