      &lt;li&gt;Draft scientific publications and BIODAS publications (books, posters, conference materials‚Ä¶).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Translate scientific documents (English‚ÄìVietnamese and vice versa).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Conduct literature reviews, search, cite, and manage references (EndNote, Zotero‚Ä¶).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Coordinate with domestic and international experts to build capacity building programs.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Act as a teaching assistant, supporting the preparation of materials for BIODAS training courses.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Perform other tasks as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
